---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
------------ Windows (XP, Vista, 7) (32 bit ONLY!*) -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

*You can use a 64 bit system, just install the 32 bit versions of Python and the other dependancies

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--> What you need to install for the script to work:

 - Python 2.7.2 - http://python.org/ftp/python/2.7.2/python-2.7.2.msi
 - pywin32 Build 217 - http://sourceforge.net/projects/pywin32/files/pywin32/Build%20217/pywin32-217.win32-py2.7.exe/download
 - SendKeys 0.3 (Python 2.7) - http://web.dyfis.net/SendKeys-0.3.win32-py2.7.exe 
 - python-netifaces (Use command 'easy_install netifaces' in Python shell to install)

