---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
------------ Linux/Unix using XLib, XTest ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--> Depandancies:

 - Python 2.7.2
 - python-virtkeys
 - xlib (*nix only)
 - xtest (*nix only)
 - python-netifaces

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--> Running the script:

 - Edit settings.conf to your liking (To make it easier to remember the server IP, set the host value to the IP you will be connecting 
   to. That way it will be displayed everytime you run the script reminding you of what the IP address is. Use the command 'ifconfig' 
   in a terminal to find the IPv4 address of your network connection and copy it into the config file)
 - Run the script using the command: 'python server.py'
 - To run the server in the the background (no open windows need to stay open) run the script inside a 'screen'. 
   Initialize/Unhide Command: 'screen -R boip-server', once inside the screen, run the script normally
   Hide Current Screen: Press 'Ctrl + A + D'
 - Press 'Ctrl + C' when the script is visibly running in the current terminal window to exit the script

